name footnotehyper
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc A hyperref aware footnote environment
longdesc This package provides a footnote environment allowing verbatim
longdesc material and a savenotes environment which captures footnotes
longdesc across problematic environments. It is a successor to the
longdesc footnote package by Mark Wooding which had various
longdesc compatibility issues with modern packages (hyperref, color,
longdesc xcolor, babel-french).
